The basic package is sold in Switzerland for sFr. 450.-, the extension
package costs sFR. 200.-. Please contact A+L AG if you are living outside
of Switzerland.

For those, who want know in advance what they will buy, or which don't want
to buy anything, but have to write some smaller Modula-2 program (e.g.
for some school work), a freely distributable demo version was produced.
The compiler contains some restrictions, the debugger is missing and only 
a subset of the modules is included.

This demo version can be downloaded from ftp.eunet.ch [146.228.10.15]. It
is found in software/amiga/M2AmigaDemoV41.lha. The readme file contained
in the archive is available separately as M2AmigaDemoV41.liesmich, in the
same directory.

